These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, thriller
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, lilac
1. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes grey##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre           | thriller | romance |
| Color   | lilac     | grey  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, country
1. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre         | time-travel   | horror      |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | country |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, romance
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, rowing
1. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | documentary    |
| Sport     | baseball | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, car
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Transport   | skateboard   | car |
| Sport   | tennis | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, avocado
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, fonseca
1. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the fonseca-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Food   | avocado | blueberry |
| Cigar     | fonseca    | montecristo    |

 #################################

 
